data.description: What a deal! $10,000 buyer credit at close.  Roll up your sleeves and get to work on this sweet affordable cottage home 3 bedrooms 2 baths on City Lot in Eaton Addition district. You'll love the covered front porch and the screened-in back porch, perfect for relaxing and enjoying the outdoors. The home's energy-efficient windows allow ample natural light to flood in. High ceilings and charming built-ins enhance the overall sense of space and functionality. Laminate flooring, forced air heating, main floor master,  unfinished basement. Detached garage with work/shop space and a nice fenced lot with mature trees. This delightful cottage home is a true gem that combines classic charm with ready for what ever updates you have in mind.  Don't miss your chance to make this dreamy cottage your very own home sweet home. Motivated seller.
